over a period of many years -

181
00:18:36,102 --> 00:18:40,813
my Gainsborough, Ming vases.
Priceless!

182
00:18:40,899 --> 00:18:45,859
They are objects which l feel
reflect my personality,

183
00:18:45,947 --> 00:18:48,153
like the Japanese fighting fish -

184
00:18:48,240 --> 00:18:51,279
beautiful, graceful, elegant...

185
00:18:51,371 --> 00:18:53,613
yet single-minded of purpose

186
00:18:53,706 --> 00:18:57,372
and deadly when it finds
what it wants.

187
00:18:57,460 --> 00:19:02,586
This particular one
is valued at over $20,000.

188
00:19:02,676 --> 00:19:05,298
A luxury item, to be certain,

189
00:19:05,388 --> 00:19:09,302
but l am a man who appreciates
the finer things in life.

190
00:19:09,391 --> 00:19:13,473
