every vital organ.

201
00:19:52,525 --> 00:19:56,226
- The salt water preserved him.
- So they...

202
00:19:56,322 --> 00:19:58,812
So they got him
to the hospital in time?

203
00:19:58,907 --> 00:20:02,906
He's in the intensive care ward
at Our Lady of the Worthless Miracle.

204
00:20:02,996 --> 00:20:06,248
